OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1784468869
OL,3,CWelsh Labour leader 'expects tension'
OL,4,Cbetween Andy Burnham and Plaid
OL,6,FWelsh Labour's new leader Ken Skates
OL,7,Fsaid he "would expect tensions to
OL,8,Fcome" between Andy Burnham, the next
OL,9,FUK prime minister, and the Welsh
OL,10,FGovernment.
OL,12,FIt comes as the former Manchester
OL,13,Fmayor was officially announced as the
OL,14,Fnew leader of The Labour Party at a
OL,15,Fspecial conference on Friday (17 July)
OL,16,Fafter receiving 379 MP nominations.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/12
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
