FL,435,430,260,120,000,100
PN,43402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1784468869
OL,3,CWelsh Labour leader 'expects tension'
OL,4,Cbetween Andy Burnham and Plaid
OL,6,FSpeaking at the conference, Ken Skates
OL,7,Ftold ITV News that whilst Andy
OL,8,FBurnham's vision looked positive for
OL,9,FWales, tension is likely between
OL,10,FLabour in Westminster and Plaid Cymru
OL,11,Fin the Senedd.
OL,13,FHe said: "Andy's got an incredible
OL,14,Fvision for the UK and for Wales as
OL,15,Fpart of the UK, making sure we get
OL,16,Fmore power to people, more power down
OL,17,Fto communities right across the UK,
OL,18,Fand decentralised power as well away
OL,19,Ffrom London.
OL,26,@uD@JOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/12
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,435,430,260,120,000,100
PN,43403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1784468869
OL,3,CWelsh Labour leader 'expects tension'
OL,4,Cbetween Andy Burnham and Plaid
OL,6,F"There may well be tension, I can
OL,7,Fimagine there will be over various
OL,8,Fissues. Let's not forget they are
OL,9,Fdifferent parties.
OL,11,F"We in the Labour movement, we are the
OL,12,Fparty of devolution. Plaid Cymru are
OL,13,Fthe party of Welsh nationalism. So,
OL,14,Fyou would expect tensions to come."
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/12
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
