FL,435,430,260,120,000,100
PN,43404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1784468869
OL,3,CWelsh Labour leader 'expects tension'
OL,4,Cbetween Andy Burnham and Plaid
OL,6,FPlaid Cymru's Westminster Leader Liz
OL,7,FSaville Roberts said while her party
OL,8,Fin Westminster and in Wales is ready
OL,9,Fto work "constructively" with the
OL,10,Fincoming Prime Minister, they want to
OL,11,Fsee a change in the relationship
OL,12,Fbetween governments.
OL,14,FShe said: "Plaid Cymru, both in
OL,15,FWestminster and in government in
OL,16,FWales, stands ready to work
OL,17,Fconstructively with the incoming Prime
OL,18,FMinister to improve the lives of
OL,19,Fpeople in Wales.
OL,26,@vD@KOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/12
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,435,430,260,120,000,100
PN,43405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1784468869
OL,3,CWelsh Labour leader 'expects tension'
OL,4,Cbetween Andy Burnham and Plaid
OL,6,F"The new Labour leader and next Prime
OL,7,FMinister must take a genuinely
OL,8,Fdifferent approach to governing if he
OL,9,Fwants to abide by his pro-devolution
OL,10,Fprinciples. After years of over-
OL,11,Fcentralised inequality, we hope this
OL,12,Fwill mark the beginning of a more
OL,13,Frespectful and productive relationship
OL,14,Fbetween Wales and Westminster.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G5/12
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,435,430,260,120,000,100
PN,43406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1784468869
OL,3,CWelsh Labour leader 'expects tension'
OL,4,Cbetween Andy Burnham and Plaid
OL,6,F"Plaid Cymru has a mandate from the
OL,7,Fpeople of Wales to demand greater
OL,8,Fdevolution, including powers over
OL,9,Frail, the Crown Estate, justice, and
OL,10,Fpolicing. Andy Burnham has talked the
OL,11,Ftalk on devolution, it's now time for
OL,12,Fhim to walk the walk and respect that
OL,13,Fmandate."
OL,15,FIn his first speech as Labour leader,
OL,16,FAndy Burnham sought to counter
OL,17,Fcriticism of him being too focused on
OL,18,FManchester by insisting he would speak
OL,19,Fup for all parts of the UK.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@IO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G6/12
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,435,430,260,120,000,100
PN,43407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1784468869
OL,3,CWelsh Labour leader 'expects tension'
OL,4,Cbetween Andy Burnham and Plaid
OL,6,FHe said: "I will be a leader for the
OL,7,Fnorth, the south, the east and the
OL,8,Fwest, plus Scotland, Wales and for
OL,9,FNorthern Ireland.
OL,11,F"Yes, the north of England has given
OL,12,Fme so much, everything, in fact.
OL,14,F"And in return, I have sought to give
OL,15,Fit the strongest voice I could.
OL,17,F"That was my job, but now I do the
OL,18,Fsame for everywhere, because I see the
OL,19,Fsame challenges everywhere I look."
OL,26,@nD@JOUsD@AOUvD@AOUyD@AOU{D@cO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G7/12
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
