PN,43408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1784468869
OL,3,CWelsh Labour leader 'expects tension'
OL,4,Cbetween Andy Burnham and Plaid
OL,6,FHe added that the Labour movement
OL,7,Fwhich backed him "heard the call from
OL,8,Fthe people of Makerfield on behalf of
OL,9,Fforgotten places everywhere up and
OL,10,Fdown this country for a return of the
OL,11,FLabour they once knew."
OL,13,FHe said that the country "needs a new
OL,14,Fpath to the one that we've been on for
OL,15,Fthe last 40 years" to make an "economy
OL,16,Fand a country that works for all
OL,17,Fpeople and places".
OL,26,@oD@ROUuD@ZOUwD@RO]wD@_OUyD@RO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G8/12
