OL,3,CWelsh Labour leader 'expects tension'
OL,4,Cbetween Andy Burnham and Plaid
OL,6,FSpeaking about what Andy Burnham's
OL,7,Fappointment means for Wales, former
OL,8,Fleader of Welsh Labour Neil Kinnock
OL,9,Ftold ITV News: "It is very very good
OL,10,Fnews.
OL,12,F"He's conscious of his national
OL,13,Fobligation, universal obligation, and
OL,14,Fthat instinct, that judgement, that
OL,15,Fconviction, will ensure that he really
OL,16,Fdoes attend to the need of every part
OL,17,Fof the united kingdom, including
OL,18,FCymru."
OL,26,@zD@GO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G9/12
