OL,3,CWelsh Labour leader 'expects tension'
OL,4,Cbetween Andy Burnham and Plaid
OL,6,FOn Wednesday (15 July) Andy Burnham
OL,7,Fwas in Cardiff taking questions from
OL,8,Fmembers of the public.
OL,10,FHe spoke about wanting to plan the
OL,11,F"biggest housing building programme
OL,12,Fsince the postwar period", and the key
OL,13,Farea he wants to spend "quite a lot of
OL,14,Fpolitical capital" on is social care.
OL,16,FBoth social care and housing are
OL,17,Fdevolved, so the Welsh Government has
OL,18,Fcontrol over in Wales.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G10/12
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
