PN,43411
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1784468869
OL,3,CWelsh Labour leader 'expects tension'
OL,4,Cbetween Andy Burnham and Plaid
OL,6,FIn his first major speech on 29 June,
OL,7,FAndy Burnham announced his plans for
OL,8,Fdevolution if he became the next prime
OL,9,Fminister.
OL,11,FAndy Burnham said he will "offer new
OL,12,Fopportunities to extend devolution"
OL,13,Fhere in Wales if he becomes prime
OL,14,Fminister but suggested that would mean
OL,15,Fmore local decision-making, not
OL,16,Fnecessarily more power for the Welsh
OL,17,FGovernment.
OL,26,@sD@[OUtD@cO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G11/12
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
