OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,435,430,260,120,000,100
PN,43412
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1784468869
OL,3,CWelsh Labour leader 'expects tension'
OL,4,Cbetween Andy Burnham and Plaid
OL,6,FAt the time, First Minister Rhun ap
OL,7,FIorwerth said he will continue to make
OL,8,F"the same positive case" for a change
OL,9,Fto Welsh devolution, but warned that
OL,10,FMr Burnham's main pledge "will mean
OL,11,Fvery little to the people of Wales".
